{"tid":1603201,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[整合行動post] 9.30 罷唔罷？做乜好？ (求幫推置頂)","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:35:22.000Z","uid":270196,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"c8cd8b6f99f94247e695e1cb567ee6796114769b","tid":1603201,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:33:22.000Z","msg":"聽日就係9.30！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港國殤前一日淪為死城</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除非你份工係關乎性命(例︰醫護消防、院舍社工)，你唔罷根本就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">自私！</span></span><br />\n講中咗唔撚開心？不服來辯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">「我高人工嫁，捐出嚟仲好啦」</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">//講咗好多次，我地最缺係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人</span></strong>，唔係錢。//</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">「我打政府工嫁，點罷呀」</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">//九月二十二日和你塞一名貿易主任被捕，該職級薪酬屬總薪級表第三十四點（每月七萬零五百九十元）至總薪級表第四十四點（每月十萬零五千一百七十五元）。//</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">「我有project/event/deadline/proposal...要跟，唔罷得」</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">//咁會唔會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">死人</span>？//</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>無影響點叫罷工？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n警暴都唔洗多講...今日9.29大大堆臥底行出嚟比你影又如何<br />\n政府有冇理過你？都唔洗講<br />\n咁你係咪仲聽日返工，不了？<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><em>問心你真係一日No Pay Leave / Sick Leave射波都唔得？<br />\n咁你根本企係政府黑警同一陣線</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">「我一個人罷工都無野做...」</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請睇下面，多你一個好多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">===活動===</div><br />\n12:00-20:00 中學生九三零再罷課 @ 遮打花園<br />\n17:00-21:00 黃大仙區聯校音樂分享會 @ 摩士公園4號公園露天劇場<br />\n18:00-19:00 禱告服侍/為香港祈禱會 @ 終審法院正門<br />\n19:30-22:00 pepe心心和你拖 @ 尖沙咀鍾樓(集合)至太子站<br />\n19:30-23:00 天水圍中學生人鏈 @ 天秀公園廣場至銀座廣場<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">如果仲有請巴打們補充...</span><br />\n另外可以各區自發商場和你唱(首選SHK或黨鐵商場)、罷買、修復連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">===上庭聲援=== (source: tg@被捕人仕關注組)</div><br />\n<ins><strong>屯門裁判法院 少年法院</strong></ins><br />\n9:30 am - 蕭XX - 管有攻擊性武器 - #0921屯門 15歲:bangbang:還押中<br />\n<ins><strong>觀塘裁判法院 3樓1庭</strong></ins><br />\n12:00 pm - 譚XX - 襲警 - #0804黃大仙<br />\n2:30 pm - 嚴XX - 襲警 - #0803黃大仙<br />\n2:30 pm - 曾XX - 襲警 - #0803黃大仙<br />\n<strong><ins>九龍城裁判法院 5樓1庭</ins></strong><br />\n2:30 pm - 劉XX - 阻差辦公 - #0803旺角<br />\n2:30 pm - 10名被告 - 非法集結、未能出示身分證 - #0803旺角 其中 15歲 蕭XX:bangbang:還押中<br />\n2:30 pm - 李XX、菲籍被告 - 非法集結 -  #0803旺角 <br />\n<strong><ins>西九龍裁判法院 4樓1庭</ins></strong><br />\n9:30 am - 吳XX - 管有攻擊性武器 - #0921屯門<br />\n<ins><strong>東區裁判法院 6樓1庭 (請再同保安cfm下)</strong></ins><br />\n2:30 pm - 6名被告 - 進入或逗留在會議廳範圍 - #0701立法會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUDdZTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUDdZTa.jpg&h=86e7cb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3eTZTb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3eTZTb.jpg&h=f63dc87d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JsOEVrw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJsOEVrw.jpg&h=e82c9101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gW8Q16x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgW8Q16x.jpg&h=c6ed387d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtagddc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdtagddc.jpg&h=f77dd2de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上面語氣可能唔係咁好，但係聽日930真係要人！<br />\nP牌推唔到 麻煩認同巴打絲打嘅幫推</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f2ae2a921bf404c76be02bd129cb7c3dc0b08d","tid":1603201,"uid":104811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:33:43.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},{"pid":"b44248ae35ab935fa90669d7e356f50e5ecf8469","tid":1603201,"uid":99871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日罷買罷市罷工罷課 你屋企要人啊"},{"pid":"9226f080acd61840ab3a3d769f6788628b7fabfa","tid":1603201,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[兩日兩個行動post] 個人建議10&middot;1行動 冇人推我11:30訓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603134</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"59fb5dd5b263e4965c9b5cb6a3a7acb4f2a25f98","tid":1603201,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:38:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4488cd2030719eb2f7bc154dcfb255312ca1801b","tid":1603201,"uid":238569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a78d961f29dc07146d64bcd65deae5c79840ea81","tid":1603201,"uid":104811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe318b98101bda36a700cc2e48192b87add8d8da","tid":1603201,"uid":140375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"大力推<br />\n熱門一個聽日行動post都無，係咪罷架到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e127feca76a2ef05471eb929055402dc8ac5b0e1"